{"tid":1543044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾on9民建聯","createTime":"2019-09-05T04:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T05:53:57.000Z","uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"595a4a570efce251ab9e0b0acf475fec558c7e8e","tid":1543044,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"如圖啦～其實佢地都唔係一兩次咁樣<br />\n呢個手法係佢地咁多年黎都係咁.將人地辛苦爭取歸於自己<br />\n但係今次大家都忍唔忍到？？？？<br />\n我地呢兩個月咁辛苦 日日都辛水辛汗 <br />\n我地無左<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼👁 2次地鐵恐襲🚝 <br />\n10條人命👺 同無數既受傷   </span></span></strong><br />\n但係佢地班柒頭就咁搶我地小小既一步<br />\n雖然呢一步唔係話太大 但係我地香港人 用命用血攞返黎<br />\n講真個句 大家有無諗過屌popo 屌林奠<br />\n不如唔差個步屌埋 垃圾民建聯 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVc3jSw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVc3jSw.png&h=ad9793e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed93234bde44eb266fc62506f9ddb013b8135537","tid":1543044,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx